pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-japan-foreign-ministers-meet-beijing-seafood-trade-agenda-2024-12-25/</guid></item><item><title>加拿大谴责中国就维吾尔族和西藏问题针对加拿大机构采取的措施</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</link><description>加拿大政府周二谴责中国对涉及维吾尔族和西藏人权问题的两家加拿大机构和20名人士采取措施。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 21:43:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/canada-condemns-chinas-steps-against-canadian-institutions-over-uyghurs-tibet-2024-12-24/</guid></item><item><title>中国药明康德将在美国限制下出售先进疗法部门</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-sell-advanced-therapies-unit-us-private-equity-firm-2024-12-24/</link><description>中国药明康德周二表示，其子公司已与美国私募股权公司 Altaris LLC 签署协议，出售其细胞和基因治疗制造部门 WuXi Advanced Therapies，交易金额未公开。</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Dec 2024 14:00:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-wuxi-sell-advanced-therapies-unit-us-private-equity-firm-2024-12-24/</guid></item></channel></rss>